BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Phase 1: Elimination \(2-4 Weeks\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Remove common trigger foods completely for 2-4 weeks until symptoms improve.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Foods to REMOVE) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.4 Td (- Gluten \(wheat, barley, rye, spelt\)) Tj ET
