BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Eggs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Soy \(tofu, soy sauce, edamame\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Corn) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (- Refined sugar and artificial sweeteners) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.4 Td (- Alcohol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514.4 Td (- Caffeine \(or reduce to 1 cup green tea\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.4 Td (- Processed and packaged foods) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 472.6 Td (Foods to EAT Freely) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.6 Td (- All vegetables \(especially leafy greens\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.6 Td (- Most fruits \(limit high-sugar tropical fruits\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 428.6 Td (- Lean proteins: chicken, turkey, fish) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 414.6 Td (- Healthy fats: olive oil, avocado, coconut oil) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 400.6 Td (- Gluten-free grains: rice, quinoa, millet) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 386.6 Td (- Nuts and seeds \(if tolerated\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 372.6 Td (- Herbs, spices, and bone broth) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 342.8 Td (Phase 2: Reintroduction \(6-8 Weeks\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 324.8 Td (Reintroduce one food at a time, every 3-4 days, and monitor reactions.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 297.0 Td (Reintroduction Protocol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 281.0 Td (- Day 1: Eat the test food 2-3 times) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 267.0 Td (- Days 2-3: Remove the food and monitor symptoms) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 253.0 Td (- Day 4: If no reaction, move to next food) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 239.0 Td (- If reaction occurs: Remove food, wait until symptoms clear, then test next food) Tj ET
